data.title: Fun Outing
data.text:
I had to chance to sneak out of the house without the kids. They had just had the opening of "4 Your Entertainment." It was nice to be surrounded by such amazing pieces of art. I also follow them on Facebook, and they put out the call to local artist for various showings and events all the time, so it is nice to see them pull people in from the local community as well. 

Check out their FB page for upcoming events when you are in town
